{"tid":991933,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[日檢JLPT] 2018年第2回試驗網上成績閱覽","createTime":"2019-01-22T18:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:24:04.000Z","uid":184374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7dca0b2a0bd36c7e88d730e066532fbf5656491b","tid":991933,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"（以下為轉載電郵內容）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位考生： <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2018年第2回日本語能力試驗網上成績閱覽</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n2018年第2回日本語能力試驗成績，可按照下列時間表登入「考生登入」版面閱覽：<a href=\"https://www.japanese-edu.org.hk/JLPT/Login\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japanese-edu.org.hk%2FJLPT%2FLogin&d=3wqZvlkJNHiQMS%2BqJADsWgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3d3d9a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.japanese-edu.org.hk/JLPT/Login</a><br />\n <br />\n網上閱覽成績日期：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">　N1, N2 及 N3  &hellip;&hellip;　2019年1月23日（星期三）早上9時開始<br />\n　N4 及 N5      &hellip;&hellip;　2019年1月23日（星期三）早上11時開始</span><br />\n <br />\n各級成績最後閱覽日期：2019年3月31日（星期日）<br />\n <br />\n成績單及合格証書於3月上旬開始的指定期間內可供領取，本會將於2月下旬寄出「領取成績通知書」，為免郵誤，考生請於1月31日前登入以上網頁查看聯絡地址是否正確。若有需要，請自行更改，多謝合作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n如有任何查詢，請致電：2866-9991或以電郵：jlpt-info@japanese-edu.org.hk與本會聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n香港日本語教育研究會<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.japanese-edu.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.japanese-edu.org.hk&d=3wqZvlkJNHiQMS%2BqJADsWgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=49ac464c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.japanese-edu.org.hk</a>"},{"pid":"79982b98a8250311eaf506d967ed060ae699f64b","tid":991933,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:10:46.000Z","msg":"半年前N5合格之後，返工忙到無時間溫書，最後今次裸考N4+N3。好驚唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de32e2626ec775f177008f20dca823417983b3a","tid":991933,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79982b98a8250311eaf506d967ed060ae699f64b","tid":991933,"uid":